### Report API Test
### Lưu ý: Thay thế {token} bằng JWT token thực tế

### ========================================
### 1. TEST CUSTOMER REPORT API
### ========================================

### 1.1 Lấy báo cáo cho Customer (tất cả)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Report/customer
Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 1.2 Lấy báo cáo cho Customer - Search theo Username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Report/customer?username=customer1
Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 1.3 Lấy báo cáo cho Customer - Search theo BookingId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Report/customer?bookingId=1
Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 1.4 Lấy báo cáo cho Customer - Search kết hợp Username và BookingId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Report/customer?username=customer1&bookingId=1
Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
Content-Type: application/json

###

